data.description: This Dean Pierce townhome is close to the University campuses & medical district and is close to the Loop for easy access to the rest of Lubbock.  Living and dining room have 20' coiffured ceilings. Dining room has built-ins with a skylight. Living room has granite bar with lighted cabinets. Kitchen features stainless appliances and a granite island. Huge isolated master downstairs with fireplace and French doors opening onto a private garden w/ pergola. His & her baths and dressing rooms w/built-ins, air Jacuzzi and walk through shower. Living space includes an office on main floor. Second floor has 2 bedrooms & bath as well as a cedar lined boot closet. There is a finished basement. Carport for 3 vehicles with cabinets. Storage shed in the back.
